-- Croatia’s Adris Grupa May Buy Triglav Insurer, Finance Reports
-- B y   B o r i s   C e r n i
-- 2012-10-02T07:26:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-02/croatia-s-adris-grupa-may-buy-triglav-insurer-finance-reports.html
Adris Grupa d.d.  of  Croatia  may buy
 Zavarovalnica Triglav (ZVTG)  d.d., Slovenia’s biggest insurer, Finance
newspaper  reported , citing people from the Croatian company it
didn’t name.  The Rovinj-based tobacco firm with interests in tourism,
said it’s considering entering the insurance market, the
Ljubljana-based newspaper said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Boris Cerni in Ljubljana at 
 bcerni@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  